their food expenses are a source of headaches for Lawrence.\nOne day, as Lawrence is going about his fur side business to further fill the family's coffers, a slight incident occurs.\nTo further complicate things, Holo saunters in with quite the feast.\n\nThis is a VR Animation of Spice and Wolf: Spring Log, sequel to the original Spice and Wolf VR animation.\nThe game has a 30 minute story and a game mode where you can watch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\""}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Icon_mobile.png", "id": "1064913614018317", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75375083_1064913617351650_8414523728123351065_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hlsnEcnrWRgQ7kNvgHy-sPV&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBSmrYyOjWmuQaMMvm64W6QEyRl7LdexxemNqKqtXTl5g&oe=67123C51"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Landscape.png", "id": "888092388709773", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75221313_888092392043106_3388339122400482554_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YTBfA9YckM4Q7kNvgHjLlsc&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDKXFJgszBnF8da5FceVbC_zQ1dTQDDxu5unsmt8Nwn-g&oe=67125F88"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_VRLandscape.png", "id": "723262801706006", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982668_723262805039339_6616665206780105350_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4mlimkaFntEQ7kNvgGkd5KZ&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDBQGzeLJpfvnGzIihB_W2dasBkZ8YCfBnf87sRvxl8yw&oe=671236A5"}, {"f