e things, Holo saunters in with quite the feast.\n\nThis is a VR Animation of Spice and Wolf: Spring Log, sequel to the original Spice and Wolf VR animation.\nThe game has a 30 minute story and a game mode where you can watch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\""}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Icon_mobile.png", "id": "4977285745675565", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974887_4977285749008898_4482133498831970937_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=j484_VYVo6UQ7kNvgFPXcbC&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD6jKYVpP-15SlzRgpjYtMK-PH8LQV59KeQaJhCbrpBQQ&oe=67125B7B"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Portrait_en.png", "id": "1115593388914444", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031366_1115593392247777_1108929082473903627_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qhJFwxCGpHAQ7kNvgE913Gz&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBdoEeZiJ7wVKD3WlPIlUPOd-jk7hnKPaC04Rk85quu5g&oe=67123184"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Hero_en.png", "id": "871157030095923", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982668_871157033429256_6789488157395094913_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WmN2o6tC0HgQ7kNvgFIgyPc&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA2WBxt1JAyckPGRPPTyRBliB3FEaFv7w4L0Z02bIUyXQ&oe=67125550"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Square_en.png", "id": "477446693254143", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974841_477446696587476_4659881486425096962_n.png?_nc_cat